overview: Zero's Strange World video starred Garrett Hill, Keegan Sauder, John Rattray, Sheldon Meleshinski, Tony Cervantes, Ben Gilley, Marisa Dal Santo, Jamie Thomas, Elissa Steamer, Donovan Piscopo, Tommy Sandoval, Dane Burman, James Brockman, Tom Asta, Chris Cole and Jamie Tancowny.
title: Strange World
